Author: throwaway767890
Text: This was very insightful, thank you. I just know that it’ll make me very uncomfortable and/or trigger me. I unfortunately get nervous and scared around anyone I deem better then me (thinner/prettier) so I don’t know if it will be helpful if I’m shutting down :(

Author: ekwater
Text: may I just say, having done group eating disorder therapy before, that there was all ranges of body shapes, sizes, weights etc.  even as a "thinner" person there (and NOT the thinnest there), I never once judged the people in larger bodies. because we were all having a shitty time and struggling. so just know that people won't laugh, and I found group therapy to be really affirming
